sample_growth_protocol_ch1: lymphocytes isolated from tonsils by ficoll gradient centrifugation
sample_extract_protocol_ch1: Omni-ATAC-seq https://www.nature.com/articles/nmeth.4396, Illumina nextera per protocol https://www.nature.com/articles/nmeth.4396
sample_data_processing: Complete processing pipeline available at https://github.com/DoaneAS/atacflow, Read adapter trimming using ngtrim, Alignment to GRCh38 using bowtie2, PCR duplicate removeal by piccard tools, Peak calling using genrich
supplementary_files_format_and_content: NarrowPeak files contain ATAC-seq peaks.bigWig files contain binned ATAC-seq fragments normalized to reads in peaks using a consensus peak atlas.

sample_growth_protocol_ch1: OCI-Ly7 cells were cultured in medium containing 80% Iscove’s Modified Dulbecco’s Medium with 20% FBS, or 90% RPMI-1640 with 10% FBS (SU-DHL-4), each supplemented with 1% glutamine and 1% penicillin/streptomycin. CRISPRi cells were generated by lentiviral transduction of pHR-SFFV-dCas9-BFP-KRAB (46911, Addgene).
sample_extract_protocol_ch1: Trizol, Illumina TruSeq stranded mRNA., Paired-end
sample_data_processing: Read adapter trimming using fastp., Transcript quantification with decoy-aware transcriptome using Salmon version 1.5.1.
supplementary_files_format_and_content: Salmon quant.sf files containing transcript quantifications.

sample_extract_protocol_ch1: Trizol, Illumina TruSeq stranded mRNA., Paired-end
sample_data_processing: Read adapter trimming using fastp., Transcript quantification with decoy-aware transcriptome using Salmon version 1.5.1.
supplementary_files_format_and_content: Salmon quant.sf files containing transcript quantifications.

sample_growth_protocol_ch1: Primary lymphocytes were isolated by gradient centrifugation and naive and germinal center B cell populations were isolated by FACS. OCI-Ly7 cells were cultured in medium containing 80% Iscove’s Modified Dulbecco’s Medium with 20% FBS, or 90% RPMI-1640 with 10% FBS (SU-DHL-4), each supplemented with 1% glutamine and 1% penicillin/streptomycin. CRISPRi cells were generated by lentoviral transduction of pHR-SFFV-dCas9-BFP-KRAB (46911, Addgene).
sample_extract_protocol_ch1: 10 million cells were fixed in 1% formaldehyde for 10 min at room temperature, and fragmentation of fixed chromatin was obtained from isolated nuclei by sonication. To enrich for short chromatin fragments (200 - 700 bp), 5μg of antibody was added to the chromatin lysate and incubated overnight at 4 °C. The following day, Dynabeads protein A was added and incubated with rotation at 4 °C for 1.5 hours. Enriched DNA was isolated through extensive wash steps, subsequent reverse cross-linking, and pu ...
sample_data_processing: Adapter trimming using Trime Galore!, Alignment using BWA., Mark duplicate reads using picard., Filtering to remove reads mapping to blacklisted regions, reads marked as duplicates and unmapped reads., Call narrowPeaks and generate fold enrichment / input bigWig files using MACS2.
supplementary_files_format_and_content: NarrowPeak file and fold enrichment / input bigWig.

sample_growth_protocol_ch1: OCI-Ly7 cells were cultured in medium containing 80% Iscove’s Modified Dulbecco’s Medium with 20% FBS, 1% glutamine, and 1% penicillin/streptomycin. CRISPRi cells were generated by lentiviral transduction of pHR-SFFV-dCas9-BFP-KRAB (46911, Addgene).
sample_extract_protocol_ch1: H3K27ac HiChIP was performed using 10 million cells., Following biotin pull-down, samples were tagmented with Tn5 and libraries were generated using 6-8 cycles of PCR amplifications. After dual size selection with Ampure XP beads, libraries size was measured by BioAnalyzer., HiSeq4000 platform on PE50 mode.
sample_data_processing: HiC-Pro was used for aligning reads and generated contact maps., mcool files were generated from validPairs files using "cooler" as part of the HiC-Pro pipeline.
supplementary_files_format_and_content: Contact maps provided as mcool files.LY7_H3K27ac_controlpooled_5000.mcool: This file represents processed files for pooled replicates samples: H3K27ac_HiChIP_OCI-Ly7_control_rep1, H3K27ac_HiChIP_OCI-Ly7_control_rep2, and H3K27ac_HiChIP_OCI-Ly7_control_rep3.LY7_H3K27ac_OCABipooled_5000.mcool: This file represents processed files for pooled replicates samples: H3K27ac_HiChIP_OCI-Ly7_OCABi_rep1, H3K27ac_HiChIP_OCI-Ly7_OCABi_rep2.

sample_extract_protocol_ch1: H3K27ac HiChIP was performed using 10 million cells., Following biotin pull-down, samples were tagmented with Tn5 and libraries were generated using 6-8 cycles of PCR amplifications. sample_data_processing: HiC-Pro was used for aligning reads and generated contact maps., mcool files were generated from validPairs files using "cooler" as part of the HiC-Pro pipeline.

sample_growth_protocol_ch1: Splenocytes from C57BL/6 mice were sorted for germinal center B cells (B220+, FAS+, GL7+) and naïve B cells (B220+, CD38+, FAS-, IgD+). B cells grown ex vivo were isolated from splenocytes using EasySep Mouse B Cell Isolation Kit (Stem Cell Technologies, catalog no. 19854).

sample_data_processing: complete processing pipeline avaialble at https://github.com/nf-core/atacseq, Read adapter trimming using ngtrim, Alignment to mm10 using bowtie2, PCR duplicate removeal by piccard tools, Peak calling using genrich
supplementary_files_format_and_content: Bigwig files contain ATAC-seq fragment density, scaled to library size.  Peak files are in narrowPeak format as output from MACS2.

sample_source_name_ch1: B cells ex vivo from splenocytes
sample_growth_protocol_ch1: Splenocytes from C57BL/6 mice were sorted for germinal center B cells (B220+, FAS+, GL7+) and naïve B cells (B220+, CD38+, FAS-, IgD+). B cells grown ex vivo were isolated from splenocytes using EasySep Mouse B Cell Isolation Kit (Stem Cell Technologies, catalog no. 19854).
sample_extract_protocol_ch1: Omni-ATAC-seq https://www.nature.com/articles/nmeth.4396, Illumina nextera per protocol https://www.nature.com/articles/nmeth.4396
sample_data_processing: complete processing pipeline avaialble at https://github.com/nf-core/atacseq, Read adapter trimming using ngtrim, Alignment to mm10 using bowtie2, PCR duplicate removeal by piccard tools, Peak calling using genrich
supplementary_files_format_and_content: Bigwig files contain ATAC-seq fragment density, scaled to library size.  Peak files are in narrowPeak format as output from MACS2.
